name: AHU-STATE

name: CFM-EXP
Comments: Calculated during operating hours only: (7.5×occupancy) + (0.06×11835) + 2353 CFM. 2353 CFM constant accounts for other spaces served by same OA damper. DCV not active outside business hours. Virtual metric.

name: CFM-DELTA
Comments: Calculated: Actual OA - Expected OA. Positive = over-ventilating negative = under-ventilating. Virtual metric.

name: DEV-PCT
Comments: Calculated: (Delta / Expected) * 100. Deviation percentage from expected OA. Virtual metric.

name: STATE
Comments: Calculated: within_tolerance | over_minor/warning/critical | under_minor/warning/critical | economizer_mode | invalid. Virtual metric.
